Package game

Contains game logic and GUI/Console specific behaviour. Game is an abstract class to act as the game environment and a super for both ConsoleGame and GUIGame.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Alex Burling(arb142), Jonathon Howe(joh29)
See Also:
Game, ConsoleGame, GUIGame
